flowchart TD
    A[Task Start] --> B{Check Source}
    B -->|Available| C[Extract Data]
    B -->|Unavailable| D[Retry Logic]
    D -->|Max Retries| E["`Alert & Log`"]
    D -->|Retry| B
    C --> F{Validate Data}
    F -->|Valid| G[Process Data]
    F -->|Invalid| H[Error Handler]
    H --> I[Clean/Fix Data]
    I --> F
    G --> J[Load Data]
    J --> K{Load Success}
    K -->|Yes| L[Complete]
    K -->|No| M[Rollback]
    M --> N[Retry Load]
    N --> J
